  "slug": "cook-sago-pearls",
  "name": "How to Make Sago Pearls",
  "recipe_type": "dessert",
  "brief_description": "How to Cook Sago Pearls? Sago pearl is an important ingredient to many desserts and beverages. It is significant to understand the proper way of cooking it",
  "cuisine": null,
  "instructions": [
    {
      "position": 1,
      "text": "Pour the water in a cooking pot. Let boil."
    },
    {
      "position": 2,
      "text": "Add-in the sago or tapioca pearls. Cover and boil in medium heat for 30 minutes. Stir every 10 minutes."
    },
    {
      "position": 3,
      "text": "Put-in the sugar. Stir. Continue to boil for 20 minutes. You can add more water if needed."
    },
    {
      "position": 4,
      "text": "Turn the heat off. For better results, let the sago or tapioca pearls remain in the cooking pot until it reaches room temperature."
    }
  ],
